# RoulettePT Spec Tests (Only)

## Import
- Postman > Import
  - RoulettePT.local.postman_environment.json
  - RoulettePT.postman_collection.json
- Environment を「RoulettePT Local」に切り替え

## Run order (spec-based)
1. Auth/Register USER
2. Auth/Register ADMIN
3. Auth/Login USER (A1)
4. Auth/Login ADMIN (A1)
5. Spin/Spin normal (SP1-SP4)
6. Spin/Spin duplicate idempotency (SP5)
7. Points/Get my balance
8. Admin/Force logout (F1)
9. Auth/Refresh USER (R1) ※ForceLogout後の挙動は仕様書の期待に合わせて確認
10. Auth/Logout USER (L1)

## Notes
- refresh_token は HttpOnly CookieのためPostmanのCookie jarで保持されます
- refresh/logout は X-CSRF-Token と Origin が必須です